Package de.intarsys.tools.attribute

Interface Summary
IAttributeSupport This interface declares support for "generic attributes".
 

Class Summary
Attribute A generic object to be used as a key with IAttributeSupport.
AttributeMap A default implementation for IAttributeSupport.
AttributeTools Tool class for handling generic attributes.
TaggedAttribute A wrapper to an Attribute to create unique keys in shared AttributeMap instances.
